name: Spiral-Only Eyes / Spiralwash Eyes - Hypnosis Concept LoRA
description:
This LoRA creates eyes with only spirals in them. AI isn't very good with spirals in general, so expect a lot of ringed eyes instead.

NOTICE: This model is not intended for txt2img. Enable this LoRA only when manually inpainting the face (with Inpaint Only Masked enabled) or using the Batch Face Swap extension (https://github.com/kex0/batch-face-swap).

modelVersions.name: v2.0
modelVersions.description:
V2.0. This was trained on more images, and for more steps. It's more consistent than the previous one in my experience.

This LoRA creates eyes with only spirals in them. AI isn't very good with spirals in general, so expect some of ringed eyes instead.

NOTICE: This model is not intended for txt2img. Enable this LoRA only when manually inpainting the face (with Inpaint Only Masked enabled) or using the Batch Face Swap extension (https://github.com/kex0/batch-face-swap).

Trained on AOM3A1 on 193 face-only cropped images for 1544 steps.
